OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey and murky start
OL,6,Fbut some spells of sunshine will
OL,7,Fdevelop, especially across the south.
OL,8,FA band of rain will move into Cumbria
OL,9,Fbefore spreading a little further
OL,10,Fsoutheast during the afternoon.
OL,11,FFeeling warm and muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe band of rain will
OL,14,Fcontinue to move southeastwards this
OL,15,Fevening, turning heavy in places.
OL,16,FTurning drier by dawn with some
OL,17,Fclearer spells developing. Another
OL,18,Fmuggy night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
