OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fspots of rain, especially over the
OL,7,Fhills. The cloud will break up
OL,8,Fthroughout the morning, leading to a
OL,9,Fmuch brighter afternoon. Feeling a tad
OL,10,Ffresher.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure builds across the region
OL,14,Fbringing plenty of dry and sunny
OL,15,Fweather throughout the period.
OL,16,FTemperatures increasing by day and
OL,17,Fnight with some very warm and humid
OL,18,Fconditions developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
